  • Packages that use edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr.spi 
    Package Description
    edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr
    Types that assemble and operate an indexing workflow, as well as CLI support therefor.
    edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr.impl
    Default implementations of ld2solr SPI.
    edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr.spi
    Types to implement to create steps in ld2solr workflow.

    Indexer
    An Indexer produces indexer heads from a particular store or source of Linked Data.
    IndexingTransducer
    An IndexingTransducer is moved in a path across an LDPath backend and executes a single indexing transformation, producing a NamedFields as the result of each execution.
